briefdescription.para: BCDS_MODULE_ID for each module in the ESSENTIALS package, used for the macros in BCDS_Retcode.h.

detaileddescription.para: usage: For a new module in this package, add a new ID value to this enum, then use it in the module's C file: #undef BCDS_MODULE_ID #define BCDS_MODULE_ID BCDS_ESSENTIALS_MODULE_ID_xxx
